&lt;/h2>&lt;p>安装
&lt;a
class="link"
href="https://github.com/hotoo/pangu.vim"
target="_blank"
rel="noopener"
>hotoo/pangu.vim&lt;/a>
&lt;/p>
&lt;p>参考：&lt;/p>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>
&lt;a
class="link"
href="https://github.com/sparanoid/chinese-copywriting-guidelines"
target="_blank"
rel="noopener"
>中文文案排版指北&lt;/a>
&lt;/li>
&lt;li>
&lt;a
class="link"
href="https://aisensiy.me/auto-update-content-in-markdown/"
target="_blank"
